text: Cryptaulax is a genus of cryptomonads in the order Cryptomonadales and the family Cryptomonadaceae. == Species == Cryptaulax akopos – Cryptaulax conoidea – Cryptaulax elegans – Cryptaulax formica – Cryptaulax longiciliatus – Cryptaulax marina – Cryptaulax taeniata – Cryptaulax vulgaris == References == == External links == * * Category:Cryptomonad genera
title: Cryptaulax (cryptomonad)
